IN RE: Matter of Foreclosure of a Deed of Trust Executed by Sheila MCLEAN Dated June 2, 2005, and Recorded in Book 1477, Page 417 et. seq., of the Franklin County Registrar of Deeds No. 201P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2017 Benjamin D. Busch, Attorney at Law, Durham. Christopher B. Karlsson, Attorney at Law, Charlotte, for Nationstar Mortgage, LLC. Shelia McLean, for McLean, Sheila.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 20th of June 2017 by Respondent in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of August 2017."
